<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>회원가입 - 서비스명</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #d9d9d9;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .signup-container {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 500px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .signup-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .signup-form {
            width: 250px;
        }

        .signup-form label {
            font-size: 12px;
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .signup-form input {
            width: 92%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #d9d9d9;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .signup-form .button-container {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .signup-form button {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            background-color: #d9d9d9;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="signup-container">
    <div class="signup-message">
        <strong>냉장고를 부탁해</strong><br>
        환영합니다!
    </div>
    <form class="signup-form" action="/refri/save" method="post">
        <label for="username">사용자 이름</label>
        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>

        <label for="email">이메일</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

        <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>

        <div class="button-container">
            <button type="submit">가입하기</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>
